; Firebase Configuration
; Filled in locally - not committed with real values.
; FIREBASE_API_KEY: Project Settings > General > Web API Key
; FIREBASE_DATABASE_URL: e.g. https://your-project-default-rtdb.firebaseio.com
; FIREBASE_DEVICE_EMAIL/PASSWORD: a dedicated Firebase Auth user for this
; device (not a personal account) - restrict it in your Realtime Database
; security rules to only its own /devices/{uid} path.
; FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET: bare bucket name, e.g. your-project.appspot.com
; (no gs:// prefix - see the storageBucket note in board-upload-latest-firmware.yml)
FIREBASE_API_KEY=
FIREBASE_DATABASE_URL=
FIREBASE_DEVICE_EMAIL=
FIREBASE_DEVICE_PASSWORD=
FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=
